        "subject": "LU-2456 lnet: DLC libyaml code",
        "message": "LU-2456 lnet: DLC libyaml code\n\nThis patch adds support for the 3rd party library libyaml.\nThis library is licensed under the MIT License.\nlibyaml is used for YAML text parsing.  Another layer, cYAML,\nwill be built on top of it to allow the building of an\ninternal representation of a YAML block which can be stored\nqueried, etc.\n\nSigned-off-by: Amir Shehata <amir.shehata@intel.com>\nChange-Id: Ie60990fdb48ba9714c2339419aefc2d723b1b1ca\n"
